{
  "stem": "1029.3",
  "chunk_idx": 3,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 11.3,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "So my grandfather kept dreaming about onions, and kind of worked into my brain about onions.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And so we were freed.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And we just didn't know what to do with ourselves.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "We couldn't eat because we were so emaciated that it was going to kill us.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "So we had to eat very light soups that we were allowed to eat.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "We-- and then everybody came down the fleck typhus, you know, from the lice and so on.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "It's typhoid fever.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "And everybody was sick as dogs.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "They took us into this hospital and with Russian nurses, and so on.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yeah, my grandparents, my mother, my grandmother, Harry, [?",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Yitka, ?] we were all delirious.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I remember the fever and everything.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And-- and then we-- we kids, and then we made some new friends.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "I had another four or five friends.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And the fever left us early.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "OK, so we left the hospital compound.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And when we left, we went outside.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "Right outside the hospital, there was the highway.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And on the highway, you could see the Russian tanks moving all the time, the American trucks, and so on.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And we hitchhiked.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And we went looting with everybody else.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "I mean, German prisoners were coming home.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "It-- it was unbelievable what was going on.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "And how we stayed alive in all this looting, I mean, I-- we were constantly on tanks.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "And we were eating chocolates from these American soldiers-- and-- unbelievable.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "And then we went into this factory.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "We-- we read German.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "You know, we knew German.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "And we knew it was a honey factory.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "Let's go in, have some honey.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "We don't know how the honey was manufactured.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "There was this emulsion, this huge vat, you know, this sticky stuff.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "It was half full.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "And I climbed up with the help of my friends.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "And I looked in.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 26,
      "text": "And I fell in.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 27,
      "text": "Luckily, when I fell in, I fell head over.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 28,
      "text": "You know, and I fell in feet first.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 29,
      "text": "And I started sinking.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 30,
      "text": "And I started screaming.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 31,
      "text": "I tell the kids, get somebody!",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 32,
      "text": "I'm dying here!",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 33,
      "text": "I'm gonna-- I'm gonna die!",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 34,
      "text": "I'm gonna drown in this honey, or whatever it was.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 35,
      "text": "Then my kids, went up, screamed.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 36,
      "text": "This Russian sergeant, the Russian sergeant came in, looked in.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 37,
      "text": "And he see what it was.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 38,
      "text": "And he got a rope.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 39,
      "text": "And I pulled myself out.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 40,
      "text": "OK, and he pulled me up, with this rope.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 41,
      "text": "And I was sticky with this honey, and this horrible feeling of-- oh.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 42,
      "text": "So then everybody, all the soldiers laughed.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 43,
      "text": "They had some sort of a celebration that night, you know, with the balalaikas, with the-- with the hand organs and stuff.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 44,
      "text": "They were dancing.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 45,
      "text": "And they washed me.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 46,
      "text": "They gave me some clothes, some, you know, Russian soldiers' uniforms.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 47,
      "text": "And ah, and we went on our way the next day.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 48,
      "text": "And we were looting.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 49,
      "text": "All my friends were stealing gold watches, you know, gold pens, any trinket, anything that shown, anything that was yellow, they stole.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 50,
      "text": "And I was also stealing the same thing.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 51,
      "text": "I was doing the same thing.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 52,
      "text": "And as I went into one of the big apartment buildings, and I went to one of the apartments, and just by chance I looked under this bed.",
      "word_count": 28
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 53,
      "text": "And lo and behold, you wouldn't believe this.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 54,
      "text": "But there was 10 kilograms of fresh onions-- you know, the hard ones in this red bag, this red, you know, rope-woven bag.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 55,
      "text": "I took this out.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 56,
      "text": "And I could think of nothing but my grandfather, and how he loved these onions, and how people, you know, need the onions, and how there's no onions anywhere.",
      "word_count": 29
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 57,
      "text": "And that-- so what I did was I took off all my clothes, all my-- I put this big thing, you know, right in front of me.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 58,
      "text": "I put all my sweaters, all my-- all my coats and everything on top.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 59,
      "text": "I got rid of my-- all my gold stuff.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 60,
      "text": "I couldn't--",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Kids said, you don't need this.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "What do you need?",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "You're going to carry those onions?",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "You're crazy.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "You're nuts.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Everything.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "Well, anyway, I-- I was like this.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And on trains, and on the-- on the trucks, I held these onions.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And I wouldn't tell anybody what it was.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And gradually, they stole my pens, and my this, my watches, my everything.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "So when we finally got home about two weeks later-- I mean, we could have died.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I mean, all the nuts going around, and all those people who were still killing.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And-- and probably they could have killed us.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "But how we-- I mean, we just didn't-- we were free.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "You know, there was no more war.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "There was-- so anyway, we got home.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "By that time, the parents, and my grandfather, everybody was well, sort of.",
      "word_count": 13
    }
  ],
